    "analysis": "The previous step produced global aggregations (count, min/max timestamps, P95) for metric, trace, and log groups. Observations: metric/trace/log data cover 2024-01-23 06:53:00 to 2024-01-23 07:17:00 UTC which lies inside the incident window (2024-01-23 06:50:39 to 2024-01-23 07:20:39 UTC). error_logs.csv is empty. Next we must run metric-based anomaly detection using the previously computed global P95 thresholds (calculated over the full available series) and then inspect anomalies inside the incident window to narrow candidate faulty component-KPIs. This will guide trace and log analysis. No root cause concluded yet.",
